Simple UDP Server/Client for passing events to StatHat.com

---

stathat_udp_server.pl - The UDP Server
Stathat.pm - The Perl module
test.pl - A simple test program


---

Usage:

Edit stathat_udp_server.pl and change the port from 12321 to whatever you would like.

Start the server ( perl  stathat_udp_server.pl &  )

Edit Stathat.pm to change the defaults

Read the test program to see how to use module

